Package: ghostkernel-policyd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: GhostKernel OS Policy Engine
 Capability broker and permission policy engine for GhostKernel OS.

Package: ghostkernel-shardd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: GhostKernel OS Shard Manager
 Handles persona shard lifecycle and context isolation.

Package: ghostkernel-netd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd, iptables, nftables
Description: GhostKernel OS Network Daemon
 Shard-aware network policy and route manager.

Package: ghostkernel-airlockd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: GhostKernel OS Airlock Service
 Controlled inter-shard transfer pipeline with metadata sanitization.

Package: ghostkernel-auditd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
