Package: ghostkernel-updated
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: GhostKernel OS Update Daemon
 Signed and reproducible updates with rollback support.

Package: gkctl
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: GhostKernel OS Control Utility
